- Ah.

85
00:12:22.800 --> 00:12:24.933
- Hola. Yoshi.
- Yoshi.

86
00:12:24.934 --> 00:12:26.671
Yoshi. Yoshi.

87
00:12:26.672 --> 00:12:29.410
Yoshi. Yoshi.

88
00:12:29.411 --> 00:12:31.709
